text: The Irvine Historic Business District in Irvine, Kentucky is a historic district which was listed on the National Register of Historic Places in 2000. It is located at roughly the junction of Kentucky Route 52 and Kentucky Route 89 It included 28 contributing buildings and four non-contributing buildings and sites. With .
